{"tid":2033341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［檢討］點解仲有人唔識black block","createTime":"2020-05-24T15:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T16:49:36.000Z","uid":303486,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cc15dabf3ba73441ab16e444a50e188efacad3e0","tid":2033341,"uid":303486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:00:08.000Z","msg":"其實已經有好多手足都開過post提bb有咩要注意<br />\n但眼見今日仲係有好多新手前線做唔足<br />\n唔係露耳就露紋身<br />\n最離譜見到有手足就咁街坊裝去搬雪糕筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n.<br />\n唔該大家 真係唔好嫌麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">試過有案例就係因為手足bb做得好 <br />\n搵唔到證據證明佢做過啲咩 最後告唔入先冇事</span></span></strong><br />\n.<br />\n齋行街買嘢食嘢嘅話理得你着成點<br />\n但落得場想做嘢嘅就要遮好啲自己<br />\n街坊裝嘅就做番街坊要做嘅嘢 <br />\n報哨又好嗌口號又好<br />\n.<br />\n個人認為會出現呢個問題有兩個原因<br />\n一嚟係真係忽視咗bb嘅重要性<br />\n二嚟係落場前未諗好自己定位<br />\n.<br />\n原因一嘅 上面有講點解要bb <br />\n都係覺得冇所謂嘅 咁我祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原因二嘅<br />\n預早諗定自己落場有咩目標要達成 想做咩職位<br />\n再帶相應嘅裝備 其他多餘嘢就唔好理 <br />\n當日專注做好你assign俾自己嘅task<br />\n帶定兩套衫都好重要 一套bb一套出街衫<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">除非情況真係好危急<br />\n唔係唔該你換咗bb先好做嘢</span></span></strong><br />\n呢啲嘢衰咗就係衰咗 <br />\n俾人影到 你分分鐘就狗搵上門or焗住要着草<br />\n手足少一個就係少一個<br />\n想留住條命嚟光復香港嘅就麻煩做番足呢嘅基本嘢"},{"pid":"e463e0968f31477b56708f208754e5394d1f87cc","tid":2033341,"uid":761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"有帽風褸已經得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930fb3b04bd431bbe605e6e21a28b50fcd50b778","tid":2033341,"uid":183685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:01:28.000Z","msg":"Agger, reqlly need to protect yourselves well"},{"pid":"c01e3795086ae52ce17891e239c21f1af27db4df","tid":2033341,"uid":303486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:01:29.000Z","msg":"我都知講呢啲好噆氣 但都真係仲有好多手足做唔足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffa57a840ba088b68f8aa1bade930a93dd6b65e","tid":2033341,"uid":303486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:02:09.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁 覺得有用嘅麻煩幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39512f49e065540baf6d9f670f296cce7b567776","tid":2033341,"uid":124134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:02:28.000Z","msg":"【拋磚引玉】我地仲有兩個低風險大技可以用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2033288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2033288</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"27b3e6d6f0d5336cd8921560a17dc1e0be2d6f35","tid":2033341,"uid":303486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e463e0968f31477b56708f208754e5394d1f87cc","tid":2033341,"uid":761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"有帽風褸已經得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:06:18.000Z","msg":"啱呀 一笠上身就搞掂<br />\n再着條黑褲喺入面<br />\n要做嘢就笠風褸+除面褲"},{"pid":"6b0f1bbbe8dbc17ba148d49a6eaf9d2470323c02","tid":2033341,"uid":303486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:08:15.000Z","msg":"欣賞多咗新手上前線 但做嘢前都要諗一諗<br />\n得個勇字係唔夠㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid